{"tid":2060994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場：金管局批准中銀將客戶資料轉交廣西南寧的全資附屬公司！！","createTime":"2020-06-12T05:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T00:58:31.000Z","uid":22556,"like":8,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bbfcb69812995ff4621a3157ddc6d331d532bbc1","tid":2060994,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:16:41.000Z","msg":"《立場新聞》獲悉，中銀香港打算把部分處理及審查客戶資料的工作，轉交由位於廣西南寧的全資附屬公司負責，並獲得金管局批准，惟中銀客戶是否清楚知道自己的個人資料文件，包括資產借貸等都「被送中」則成疑問。中銀香港回應指，該行嚴格遵守香港相關法規及監管要求，妥善處理客戶個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，「被送中」的中銀客戶資料包括開戶及借貸文件。相關的文件處理和客戶盡職審查重檢工作，都會由中銀香港全資附屬公司 &mdash; 中銀金融服務（南寧）有限公司處理，這意味著大量香港客戶個人及資產資料「送中」。<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E4%B8%AD%E9%8A%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6%E5%80%9F%E8%B2%B8%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%A4%E5%BB%A3%E8%A5%BF%E9%99%84%E5%B1%AC%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%99%95%E7%90%86-%E9%87%91%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%258A%2580%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%2580%259F%25E8%25B2%25B8%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%2596%2587%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E9%2599%2584%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586-%25E9%2587%2591%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2587%2586%2F&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0vUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=b9a9eec1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%258A%2580%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%2580%259F%25E8%25B2%25B8%2